<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4322517>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Map of northern Madagascar showing reliable locality records of Uroplatus fangorn sp. nov., U. fivehy sp. nov., and their closest relative, U. finiavana. Colors in map show remaining primary vegetation following the Madagascar Vegetation Mapping Project carried out from 2003–2006 (Moat & Smith 2007); green is humid forest (rainforest), reddish tones are deciduous forest and spiny forest-thicket." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4322517/files/figure.png" .

